rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0001
rows.name:
You after something?
This is Trigo's number one farm.

rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0002
rows.name:
All the Gulan folk working here at
Kloom Farm are my own family.

rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0003
rows.name:
We've been supporting the farming
industry in Trigo for generations.
A heck of a lot of generations.

rows.label: tlk41700122_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Since you're here, why don't you take
a few of our vegetables as a souvenir?
